    <item>
      <title>日元在日本央行和美联储宣布降息前保持 2022 年以来最大月度涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/yen-holds-onto-biggest-monthly-gain-since-2022-before-boj-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元守住了一年半以来的最大月度涨幅，投资者焦急地等待央行周三做出的决定，而这一决定可能会延续日元的涨势，也可能引发日元的逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/yen-holds-onto-biggest-monthly-gain-since-2022-before-boj-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:05:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
